column5: Bro Valo tonight? We need a 5th for the rank push.
Give me 10 mins. Just finishing dinner.
GGs man. That last clutch was insane.
You coming to the canteen? Everyone is here.
Nah man. Stuck with Priya at that alley cafe. Don't tell Anjali.
Professor is taking attendance. Where are you?
Proxy laga de bhai. I'm with Priya again.
Party at Vicky's tonight. You in?
Anjali is dragging me to some family dinner. Fs in the chat.
Bro did you finish the OS assignment?
Halfway done. Will send you the zip by tonight.
Did you see the new iPhone leaks?
Yeah looks mid. Not worth the kidney.
Bro Anjali asked me if you were with me on Friday night.
What did you say??
I told her we were at the lab. You owe me a beer.
You're a lifesaver. Dinner on me this weekend.
Coming for the cricket match screening?
Can't. Anjali is suspicious. I need to play it safe today.
Send me the notes for the ML quiz. I'm cooked.
Check the Discord. Uploaded everything there.
Just saw you at the mall. Who was that girl? Not Anjali.
Keep it down bro. That was Priya. Delete this message.
Saturday concert is still on right?
100%. Anjali is mad about some wedding but I'm not missing this.
Bro the bass at this concert is crazy!! Where are you?
Near the stage. See you at the exit in an hour.
Hackathon prep starts tomorrow. Don't be late to the lab.
I'll be there. Need to get away from all the drama anyway.
